abstract: This new feature on City Room aims to collect and curate items of interest related to the Occupy Wall Street protests here and around the globe.
snippet: This new feature on City Room aims to collect and curate items of interest related to the Occupy Wall Street protests here and around the globe.
lead_paragraph: The Occupy Wall Street protests have inspired songs (if not an anthem) and marriage proposals, demonstrations across the globe, and a daily outpouring of reactions and interpretations that this new feature on City Room aims to collect and curate.
